,NULL,'','100 syringes',7),(43,'Bjain Pharmaceuticals Pvt Ltd','Bjain Pharmaceuticals Pvt. Ltd A-98, Sector 63, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201307',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-23 18:18:08',NULL,NULL,'Bjain Agnus Castus Dilution is a well-known homoeopathic remedy for sexual and rheumatic troubles. It is also an excellent homoeopathy remedy for itching, especially in the eyes. It is helpful for complaints that arise from the abuse of tobacco. | Key Ingredients: Agnus castus | Key Benefits: It helps improve cognitive functions It is effective for abdominal complaints such as the swollen, sore abdomen, soft receding stools and fissures in the anus It helps with urethral discharges in men with an absence of sexual desire This remedy also aids Scanty menses, white discharge and poor milk production in women It contains anti-inflammatory properties and improves the overall well-being of the body | Directions for use: 10 to 15 drops in ¼ cup of water, three times a day, 10 minutes before or after meals or as prescribed by the physician. | Safety Information: Read the label carefully before use Keep out of the reach of children Store in a cool and dry place Keep away from direct sunlight',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','100 ml Dilution',7),(44,'Carmine County Pvt Ltd','S-10/14 B, III F, Jogabai Extension, Jamia Nagar, Okhla, New Delhi - 110025',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-23 18:18:08',NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','30 gm Tea',7),(45,'Hindustan Syringes & Medical Devices Ltd','901-902, Narian Manzil , 23, Barakhamba Road New Delhi-110001 (India)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-23 18:18:08',NULL,NULL,'Dispovan 50ml Syringe is manufactured as per IS:10258/ ISO:7886-1. Ribbon packaged, dispo van syringes with needles mounted on top are synonymous with quality. Salient features of Dispovan 50ml Syringe: Barrels are made of nontoxic, medical-grade polypropylene compatible with any medication. The tip of the barrel 