regular monitoring of blood glucose levels for diabetic patients. | Product Specifications and Features: | SmartLIGHT Feature: provides you with an instant indicator of your blood glucose results, so you know whether they are within (green), above (amber), or below (red) your target range | Highly accurate: The Contour Plus One system exceeded the minimum accuracy requirements of the ISO 15197:2013 standard | Fewer Strip Wastage: Second chance sampling allows you to add more blood when the first sample is not enough It connects to the free Contour Diabetes app The Contour Diabetes app syncs automatically with the meter to upload all blood glucose readings to an electronic diary | Indication: Diabetes Mellitus | Compatible With: Contour Plus test strips and Contour Diabetes app | Directions for Use: Insert the test strip with the grey square end facing the meter (this will automatically turn on the meter) Immediately add blood to the test strip Your result is displayed (after marking as fasting, before/after a meal or no note) | Safety Information: Read the label carefully before use Keep out of reach of children Avoid any physical damage Store in a clean and dry place Check the strips are within their expiry date Make sure to wash and dry your hands before testing | Quick Tips: Every time you start to use a new box of test strips, make sure to calibrate your meter Do not squeeze your finger when taking a blood drop sample | Frequently Asked Questions: | What is the smartLIGHT feature? And what do the colours mean? The smartLIGHT feature on the CONTOURPLUS ONE meter gives instant feedback on your blood glucose results. It immediately identifies your results as above, below or within the target range to help you make decisions. This feature can be switched off if you prefer not to use it. Green = within the target Amber = above target Red = below target | What is Second-Chance sampling? If your first sample is insufficient to take a blood glucose reading, Second-Chance sampling lets you apply more blood to the same strip instead of using a new one. This may help you avoid pricking your finger again and waste fewer strips (and lancets).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','1 Unit',1),(48,'Rgn Foods Pvt Ltd','Unit No. 202, 2nd Floor, IJMIMA Imitation Jewellery Market CSL, Off. Link Road, Malad (West), Mumbai - 400064',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-23 18:24:09',NULL,NULL,'Cholas Omega-3 Chocolate These chocolates are healthy with omega -3 to contain 200 mg per pcs. The Omega-3 chocolates are healthy nutrition chocolates beneficial for health and especially healthy for children. The flavanols in chocolate are good for lowering blood pressure and improving blood flow. These chocolates help to prevent free radical damage and may be beneficial for the skin. | Key Ingredients: Sugar Edible vegetable fat Cocoa solids Milk solids and emulsifiers (INS 491, INS 322) Natural (vanilla) flavouring substance | Key Benefits: Chocolate has a wide variety of powerful antioxidants and may help improve blood flow and lower blood pressure It may also lower the risk of heart disease, benefit the skin and protect against free radicals Chocolate includes components that aid in its absorption, it is an excellent meal to supplement with omega-3 Omega-3 contains natural anti-inflammatory properties and is a health-boosting powerhouse that improves mood, joint and heart health | Directions For Use: Use as directed on the label. | Safety Information: Store in a cool and dry place Read the label carefully before use Do not use if the seal is missing or damaged',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','250 gm Unit',1),(49,'Natural Healthcare','Ist Floor, Shoe Market, Sanjay Place, Agra-282002 (U.P.)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-23 18:36:33',NULL,NULL,'Fasczo Vita X for Men\'s for Increase Stamina Oil It is formulated with ashwagandha, vang bhasma and other ingredients that help relieve stress and fatigue, increase stamina, and enhance blood circulation. It\'s a natural health supplement with potent ingredients that help improve energy levels, muscle strength and vitality. It helps to elevate your mood and balance male hormones. | Key Ingredients: Withania somnifera Foenieulum vulgare Vang bhasma Exparagus adscenns Dhatriloha Sesamum indicum | Key Benefits: It helps to improve your stamina, strength and vitality Ashwagandha helps to reduce stress, anxiety and fatigue It may enhance the energy levels and physical performance of men It helps to elevate your mood, improve blood circulation and balance male hormones | Directions For Use: Read the label carefully before use. | Safety Information: Read the product label carefully before use Store in a cool and dry place away from direct sunlight Keep out of reach of children',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','15 ml Oil',7),(50,'VLCC Personal Care Limited','VLCC Health Care Limited , M-14, Greater Kailash II Commercial Complex, New Delhi – 110048, India',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-23 18:44:07',NULL,NULL,'VLCC Insta Glow Oxygen Bleach makes the skin look fairer, radiant and healthy in just about 15 minutes. It bleaches facial hair to match the skin tone. | Key Ingredients: Hydrogen Peroxide Polyquaternium Compound Powder Activator: Persulphates Pre Bleach Cream: Glycerin, Silicon Blend, Allantoin, Acetyl Tetrapeptide | Key Benefits: Due to release of nascent oxygen this bleach has a unique gas flushing action Throughly cleanses the skin, unclogs the clogged pores | Directions For Use Make sure that the bleach and the activator powder are mixed in the ratio of 7:1 Apply the bleach on your face then keep it for 10 minutes if you have deep skin Keep it for 15 minutes for whitish skin and a bit longer if you have fair skin Bleach should be used once in every 2-3weeks Or use as directed by the physician | Safety Information: Patch test is recommended for first time users Do not use soap for 5 hours after the bleach Re